parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Auto Idle Stop system can cause the vehicle to stall or not restart, leading to safety risks, especially when stuck in traffic or at intersections.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or shuts down while stopped at a red light or stop sign
and the vehicle may require a jump start to restart.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the infotainment system can cause distractions while driving, leading to safety risks, and can also affect the backup camera and other safety features.
symptoms: The infotainment screen goes black or shuts off
the system produces loud crackling or popping sounds
and the backup camera and other features may not function.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of sensors can cause the vehicle to brake suddenly or unnecessarily, leading to safety risks, and can also affect the backup camera and other safety features.
symptoms: The front and rear sensors trigger unnecessarily
the low tire sensor goes off despite no low tire
and the backup camera may not function properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the key fob can cause the vehicle to lock or unlock unexpectedly, leading to safety risks, especially when children or pets are inside the vehicle.
symptoms: The vehicle locks or unlocks unexpectedly
the key fob battery may drain suddenly
and the vehicle may require emergency assistance to unlock.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: False Collision Warnings and Unwanted Braking
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The false activation of the collision mitigation system can cause sudden and unexpected braking, which can lead to accidents, rear-end collisions, and loss of control, especially on high-speed roads.
symptoms: The vehicle's collision mitigation system activates unnecessarily
displaying warnings and/or applying the brakes even when there are no obstacles or vehicles in front of the vehicle. This can occur on two-lane roads
and can happen at various speeds.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the multipurpose camera can cause the malfunction of various safety systems, including the collision mitigation system, lane departure warning, and adaptive cruise control, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: causing the malfunction of various safety systems

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause the loss of braking ability, which can lead to accidents and injuries.
symptoms: causing the loss of braking ability
and/or displaying warnings and/or applying the brakes unnecessarily.
